:"第二度無保皇黨咩？<br />\n根本係飯民自己放棄，以啟德兩條邨為例，民協民主黨走人，毛孟靜劉小麗有冇考慮補位呢？<br />\n明眼人都睇到呢幾年係飯民唔主動出擊，比北京切完一忽又一忽。<br />\n劉小麗仲話入議會積小勝成大勝，真係活係自己同溫層，完全離地!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"第二度都有 但呢邊係醫番嘥藥費<br />\n明知佢地膚淺層次低而你又資源唔夠鬥唔到錢多物資多<br />\n好似養二奶 明知佢鍾意手袋珠寶 你又無乜錢嘅 你都知你根本滿足唔到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪好似民協咁止蝕離場囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好現實 大家都係講錢"},{"pid":"a821813b73336a83c61b416439da8906d8fbff6c","tid":721744,"uid":2613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/125111_aab5ce7ca8ba75a710869d12701d23eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F125111_aab5ce7ca8ba75a710869d12701d23eb.png&h=80aa48b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上屆嘅票數<br />\n根本就係姚松炎on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本土派嘅票全部冇俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1a502ffe41a01f6ccfe17f505bab4490dd45ff","tid":721744,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a821813b73336a83c61b416439da8906d8fbff6c","tid":721744,"uid":2613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/125111_aab5ce7ca8ba75a710869d12701d23eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F125111_aab5ce7ca8ba75a710869d12701d23eb.png&h=80aa48b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上屆嘅票數<br />\n根本就係姚松炎on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本土派嘅票全部冇俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"土共嘅離間計做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e74d04db63018d665d11b09b